Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:10.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To catch the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Change the color of the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be the apple of one's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:15.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Keep one's eye on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eye is a passive vessel\Nthat collects visual information,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,while at times it also shows determination and emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:31.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is an active organ that displays such\Nthoughts in a kind of symbolic language.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eyes speak as much as the mouth does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is truly a phrase that describes the eye accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And this is its true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That man, I'm sure he came here before...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder what business he has today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did Hotori do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um... Sensei, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it, Arashiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After school, you came all the way to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You must be in love with me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Huh?" he said! Straightforward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no pulse to this romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Vitals: heart rate, breathing, blood pressure, all zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei, are you not married?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so handsome, it's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You make your own lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once it goes into the stomach, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, shoo, shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't go putting the moves on him\Nwithout any permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:05.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The customer belongs to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.92,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama, paper, paper.\N{\rSubtitle}The customer belongs to everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.38,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama, paper, paper.\N{\rSubtitle}There's an order!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:08.58,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama, paper, paper.\N{\rSubtitle}You said there was no pulse!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You said there was no pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What business do you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:17.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I refuse any extracurricular activity that's not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,While sorting through articles left by my grandfather,\NI found something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you ignoring my moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Actually, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A drawing? It's a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:38.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It looks like a normal portrait to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What don't you understand about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...this is a very unique drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:50.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone says that it's an ordinary drawing,\Nso why are you the only one saying otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know, you're trying to go along with what\Nyour teacher is saying to attract his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You little brat, pretending to be grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, it's 20% true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This canvas is totally square.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aren't drawings usually longer on the length or width?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:08.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Indeed, this drawing has an aspect ratio of 1:1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In other words, a square.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good, Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:22.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I brought this here, anticipating you'd be able\Nto catch something out of the ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To me, you are a special existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my... But I'm still in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're interpreting this to your advantage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The person who drew this picture is my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:39.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He was the youngest of three brothers,\Nand he was a starving artist when he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My grandfather liked to gamble\Nand didn't leave much of an inheritance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but he did leave many paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After my grandfather died,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,his pieces were split evenly three ways amongst\Nhis brothers and bereaved family; my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And... the real problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,this other drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Four eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,According to the label on the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think these are my grandfather's self-portraits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The titles of both drawings are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Eye"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Eye"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:21.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did my grandfather draw such strange pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ever since I found these drawings,\NI can't stop thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My heart is cloudy, and I can't fathom why!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:32.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As you already know, I am a math teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's my job to think things through logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What were the feelings of the painter\Nwhen he drew this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hah! Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How could I let someone who's not the\Nconcerned party know such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa! He's gone mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But, based on accurate guesses,\Nit is possible to hypothesize an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama, you like mystery novels, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes! I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I want to ask you to deduce\Nwhy this drawing was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At all costs, I want you to come up with\Na reason that I can agree with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really, what a troublesome teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you think the other way around, because of that\Ntroublesome personality he'll never marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a chance to get him. Right, Hotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:35.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enough about the teacher.\NDon't bother me while I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, were you still thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:39.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've solved the mystery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You too, Granny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My deduction... would you like to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you know the artist of this painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Post-impressionist artist, Vincent Van Gogh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:00.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The theory goes that Van Gogh's\Nunique coloring and touch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,is because that's what he was actually seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In the same way, we can explain\Nthat the grandfather saw exactly what he painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher's grandfather had astigmatism!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's quite the deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But then why'd he draw only one mouth and nose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Head Maid! This girl makes me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The other picture's a regular drawing, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's weird that eyes increase and decrease in numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking hard enough, Hotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you should use backwards reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher said his grandfather left many drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, for the teacher to think that that particular\Ndrawing was weird, the rest were not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Landscapes and still life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Out of many normal drawings,\Nonly that one piece was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well... that must've been true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In other words, the grandfather was someone\Nwho always drew normal paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Instead of thinking why only this drawing was special,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:12.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it would make more sense to think that this\Nwas just another ordinary piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher's grandfather was a four-eyed alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When he drew that picture,\Nhe had his other two eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's amazing! What big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wha-?! You're so annoying, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Head Maid, what should we do with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hm? Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taking something normal and thinking backwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:36.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Did you use your head\Ntoo much and now it's broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:57.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When a detective laughs loudly, there's a good chance\Nthat the mystery has been solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's hear your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sensei... There are six cards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you were to split this amongst\Nthree people, how would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You give two to each person. What else would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, to divide a castella cake amongst three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'd have to cut it into three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no! There isn't a piece for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These were just hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hate those slow-paced revelations in mystery novels,\Nand that blue dolphin on my word processing software!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop lining up hints and give me\Nthe quick and simple answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is all of the hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:01.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you apply this, then you can solve\Nthe mystery of the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You try to think about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Might it be that you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why can't you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything in excess;\Nif you apply a formula then you can solve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why can't you figure it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher always looked down on me with this feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama, you should let him know soon.\NThe teacher is at his limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something Arashiyama knows that I don't...\NHow could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My thinking is like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes! Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is the true form of this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This was a die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I added the parts that were missing\Nby drawing them in myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The title "Eye" is a word play\Non his eyes and the eyes of the dice,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:14.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and so this piece can be considered to be\Nmade up of drawings with one to six eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I say it's a self-portrait worthy of a gambling grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,However, since this piece was a cube that was\Nsplit into three, it no longer fulfilled its purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and what was left in the teacher's hands\Nwere these two mystery drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mr. Client?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama seems to look intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No matter how much vinegar I drink,\NI don't become flexible, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eyes speak as much as the mouth does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eyes continue to speak the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:59.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but whether one can understand their words\Ndepends on if that one has an eye for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:07.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I talked to my relatives, just like Arashiyama said,\NI found the remaining four drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:13.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I took into consideration my grandfather's intentions\Nand reconstructed the piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"...which I give you as a token of my appreciation."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do by making this\Nstore tighter than it already is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we hang something like this in here,\Nwe'll scare the customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.79,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!\N{\rSubtitle}If we hang something like this in here,{\r}\N{\rSubtitle}we'll scare the customers!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher went out of his way to give me this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then put it up in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Poco" means "a little" in Italian, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The onion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:46.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The allyl compound oxidizes the hemoglobin\Nin the blood causing hemolytic anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So if an animal that's not a human eats it,\Nthere's the risk of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it is a human, it is said there's a\Nhealth benefit in that the blood is cleansed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,However, there is no sufficient medical data.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:03.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cutting an onion releases sulfuric allyl\Nwhich irritates the eye, producing tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:07.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but if you chill it beforehand and then cut it,\Nthe release of the sulfuric allyl is suppressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,making it less likely for tears to come out;\Nthis is the wisdom of housewives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The reason for my tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:20.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Car-rots, on-ion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,on three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Car-rots, on-ion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Car-rots, on-ion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,on three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:37.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww! I'm not a child! I can go shopping properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have a past offense,\Nso that's why you're being told this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:48.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here! Mr. Oniot! If you forget on the way, remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It makes me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to making fun of someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:57.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Carrots and onions, right?! Who messes that up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:58.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oniot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think it's correct that it's a round thing and pointy thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? Was the round thing a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? Which one was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When they go through all that trouble to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It just makes my doubting heart create\Na dark demon all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.25,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Koban!\N{\rSubtitle}It just makes my doubting heart create{\r}\N{\rSubtitle}a dark demon all the more!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:15.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It just makes my doubting heart create\Na dark demon all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koban? Koban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koban...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koban! Koban, Koban, Koban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa... What a beautiful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cross-eyed, teary-eyed, to be the apple of one's eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The evil eye that hits you when you're already cursed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The eye is a mirror that reflects a person's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:50.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so if you look into one's eyes you can connect\Nto their heart and understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aha. Seeing that your voice hasn't changed yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you must be a boy of about 12 or 13 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, my, to bleach your hair blonde at that age...\NYou are so rebellious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're the one named Hotori, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The other day, I saw you run over\Na cop on your kick board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that how you address me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you say Hotori-san\Nor Big Sister or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Children that don't play right will have\Na hard time in this shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What kind of ritual is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A cat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A cat's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The phrase is used to describe one's fickle tendencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:44.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is a phrase that describes\Nhow its pupil opens wide then closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:49.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but it can also describe how the cat itself is fickle;\Nthat's how the phrase came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Further, those who own cats have at least\Nsome affinity to those fickle tendencies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:16:00.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so the term "cat's eye" applies to people\Nwho have a sort of magical attractiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's my cat. He's not coming out from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Koban" is the cat's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you name your cat Koban...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Neko ni Koban"! You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know, here's some Oniot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You mean onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:24.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not you, I'm saying why don't we\Nuse this as bait to lure him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:27.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm saying cats won't eat onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you're not supposed to let them eat onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. If a cat eats onion,\Nhe'll get stunned won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go home already. Your jokes are lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, you're making it snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I don't know why I said such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We won't tell any more bad jokes, so come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:55.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cats don't like the cold! Koban!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay, he'll come out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cats are fickle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My Koban is a good kitty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cat owners always say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I leave him alone and he catches a cold, I'll feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Despite your looks, you're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-you hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because you strangled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you strangle me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:37.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, if the owner was in a pinch,\Nmaybe it would jump out to your rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:43.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I own a dog at home, and she'll come\Nwhen I'm in a pinch, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I. Told. You! See? You get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a dog, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This climax really needs some planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't need your help anymore, so go away already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See, onions were the right answer after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Hotori! Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:14.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Capture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I call it "The Maid Cage"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:24.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Maid Cage" sounds like an adult DVD title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fresh little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, thank goodness Koban-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank good—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! Did I step on the cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is there a cat's tail somewhere on the ground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By any chance, are you searching for a tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, it might have been me,\Nbut it was an accident and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He had no tail to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's a breed called "Cymric," and they don't have tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:03.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A long, long time ago when his ancestor\Ntried to board Noah's ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the tail got caught in the door\Nand was cut off, or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh... I thought I was going to get yelled at\Nby the animal rights organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a romantic story, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But isn't that story weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:15.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koban and his ancestors are separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's like, if the dad got hurt, does\Nthe injury get passed on to the son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Stop splitting hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll say thanks for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"For now," huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were a very fresh brat until the end, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you should\Nat least tell me your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll just say Cat Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should've taught her the\N"don't make any detours" song, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:52.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Also, we should've drawn her a map...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ho-to-ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're the one I met yesterday! Cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, I thought you were a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No wonder our conversation didn't quite match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So we go to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What class are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:26.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?! Wait, I'm in Class A, too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Was there someone like this in my class? No there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should at least remember a classmate's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I knew I was going to encounter one of these some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The punch line is that "you are a ghost!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, she disappeared\Nyesterday without my noticing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so if I raised my face would it be,\Nlike, "She's not there, gyah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since she's showing up even in school,\Nthat must mean I'm totally possessed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon-senpai, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:53.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Haribara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For today's club meeting, we'll have a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just changed the rubber on this racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope it doesn't become the scythe of the\NGrim Reaper ready to chop off your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Say things like that only after you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you were older than me, weren't you, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But you look so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, again and again I apologize\Nfor being so rude, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can you forgive me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:33.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rap is not the only hip-hop, poko
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:38.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In today's Japan, the word describes\Nyoung girls who dress in uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and play the roles of British housekeepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maid Cafe, Maid Bar, Maid Reflexology,\NMaid Mahjong House...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:47.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On top of that there's a Maid Housekeeping Service,\Nwhich is a job that went full circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:50.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Its force knows no stopping as we approach the now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And right now, there are two girls\Nfighting for their honor as Maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll tell you before I send\Nyou to the Mei-do Underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:44.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There is a curse which people are falling to left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is that? Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The person cursed will transfer\Nthe curse to one person per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:50.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a loose curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At first, when one was cursed,\Nthe entire student body was cursed in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, if at first two were cursed, how long would it take\Nfor the whole student body to be cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's twice as many so half the time is five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:03.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Incorrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:07.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Next episode, Street Number Four,\N"The Equation of Curses."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were turning round and round yesterday, too, poko.
